[49m[38;5;10m+      1[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Technical Report
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      2[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      3[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Case:** LinkageError using lucene with spring redeploying on tomcat or weblogic  
